---
---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />

  <title>Dallas Roofing & Insurance Restoration | Free Roof Inspection</title>

  <meta
    name="description"
    content="Dallas roofing specialists for storm damage, roof replacement, and insurance restoration. Free inspections and insurance claim assistance."
  />

  <meta
    name="keywords"
    content="Dallas roofing, roof repair Dallas, roof replacement Dallas, storm damage roofing, insurance restoration Dallas"
  />

  <meta name="robots" content="index, follow" />

  <style>
    :root {
      --primary: #0f172a;
      --accent: #f59e0b;
      --light: #f8fafc;
      --text: #111827;
      --muted: #6b7280;
      --border: #e5e7eb;
    }

    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    html {
      scroll-behavior: smooth;
    }

    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      color: var(--text);
      line-height: 1.6;
      background: white;
    }

    .container {
      width: min(1100px, 92%);
      margin: auto;
    }

    header {
      background: linear-gradient(
        rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.92),
        rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.92)
      );
      color: white;
      padding: 100px 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    header h1 {
      font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 5vw, 4rem);
      line-height: 1.1;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      max-width: 900px;
      margin-inline: auto;
    }

    header p {
      max-width: 700px;
      margin-inline: auto;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      color: #d1d5db;
    }

    .hero-buttons {
      margin-top: 30px;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 15px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .btn {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 14px 24px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: bold;
      transition: 0.2s ease;
    }

    .btn-primary {
      background: var(--accent);
      color: black;
    }

    .btn-secondary {
      border: 1px solid white;
      color: white;
    }

    section {
      padding: 80px 0;
    }

    h2 {
      font-size: 2rem;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .section-text {
      max-width: 700px;
      margin: auto;
      text-align: center;
      color: var(--muted);
      margin-bottom: 40px;
    }

    .grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(240px, 1fr));
      gap: 20px;
    }

    .card {
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      padding: 25px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      background: white;
    }

    .card h3 {
      margin-top: 0;
    }

    .process {
      background: var(--light);
    }

    .process ol {
      max-width: 700px;
      margin: auto;
      padding-left: 20px;
    }

    .trust-bar {
      background: var(--primary);
      color: white;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      font-weight: bold;
    }

    .cta {
      background: var(--primary);
      color: white;
      text-align: center;
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 60px 30px;
    }

    form {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: auto;
    }

    input,
    select,
    textarea {
      width: 100%;
      padding: 14px;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 6px;
      font-size: 1rem;
    }

    button {
      width: 100%;
      padding: 14px;
      border: none;
      background: var(--primary);
      color: white;
      font-size: 1rem;
      border-radius: 6px;
      cursor: pointer;
    }

    footer {
      background: #f3f4f6;
      padding: 40px 20px;
      text-align: center;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }

    @media (max-width: 640px) {
      section {
        padding: 60px 0;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>

  <header>
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Dallas Roofing & Insurance Restoration Specialists</h1>

      <p>
        Storm damage inspections, insurance claim assistance, roof repair,
        and full roof replacement throughout Dallas and surrounding areas.
      </p>

      <div class="hero-buttons">
        <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-primary">
          Get Free Roof Inspection
        </a>

        <a href="tel:+12145551234" class="btn btn-secondary">
          Call Now
        </a>
      </div>

      <p style="margin-top:25px;font-size:0.95rem;">
        ✔ Free inspections &nbsp;
        ✔ Insurance claim support &nbsp;
        ✔ Local Dallas roofing experts
      </p>
    </div>
  </header>

  <div class="trust-bar">
    Licensed • Insured • Storm Damage Specialists • Insurance Restoration
  </div>

  <section>
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Roofing Services</h2>

      <p class="section-text">
        Professional roofing and storm restoration services designed to help
        homeowners recover quickly after hail, wind, and storm damage.
      </p>

      <div class="grid">

        <div class="card">
          <h3>Storm Damage Inspections</h3>
          <p>
            Detailed inspections with documentation for insurance claims.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <h3>Insurance Claim Assistance</h3>
          <p>
            We help homeowners navigate the insurance restoration process.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <h3>Roof Repair</h3>
          <p>
            Fast repairs for leaks, missing shingles, and damaged roofing systems.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <h3>Roof Replacement</h3>
          <p>
            Full roof replacement using high-quality roofing materials.
          </p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="process">
    <div class="container">

      <h2>Our Process</h2>

      <p class="section-text">
        A simple process focused on fast inspections, accurate documentation,
        and quality roofing work.
      </p>

      <ol>
        <li>Schedule your free roof inspection</li>
        <li>We inspect and document storm damage</li>
        <li>Insurance claim assistance and adjuster coordination</li>
        <li>Roof repair or full replacement completion</li>
      </ol>

    </div>
  </section>

  <section>
    <div class="container">

      <h2>Common Roof Problems We Find</h2>

      <div class="grid">

        <div class="card">
          <h3>Hidden Hail Damage</h3>
          <p>
            Damage often invisible from the ground after severe storms.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <h3>Wind Damage</h3>
          <p>
            Missing shingles and lifted roofing materials after storms.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <h3>Roof Leaks</h3>
          <p>
            Interior water damage caused by compromised roofing systems.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <h3>Insurance Underpayment</h3>
          <p>
            Claims that fail to account for full storm-related damage.
          </p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section>
    <div class="container">

      <div class="cta">
        <h2>Is Your Roof Storm-Damaged?</h2>

        <p>
          Small roofing issues can become major repair costs if ignored.
          Schedule a free inspection today.
        </p>

        <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-primary">
          Request Free Inspection
        </a>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="contact">
    <div class="container">

      <h2>Request Free Roof Inspection</h2>

      <p class="section-text">
        Submit your information and we’ll contact you to schedule an inspection.
      </p>

      <form>

        <input
          type="text"
          placeholder="Full Name"
          required
        />

        <input
          type="tel"
          placeholder="Phone Number"
          required
        />

        <input
          type="text"
          placeholder="Property Address"
          required
        />

        <select>
          <option>Storm Damage</option>
          <option>Roof Leak</option>
          <option>Roof Replacement</option>
          <option>Insurance Claim Help</option>
        </select>

        <textarea
          rows="5"
          placeholder="Describe your roofing issue"
        ></textarea>

        <button type="submit">
          Get Free Inspection
        </button>

      </form>

    </div>
  </section>

  <footer>
    <p>
      © 2026 Dallas Roofing Partners. All rights reserved.
    </p>
  </footer>

</body>
</html>